      <title>印度储备银行表示，银行需要在危机期间利用分支机构吸收存款</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/rbi-says-banks-need-to-use-branches-to-draw-deposits-amid-crunch</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度的银行应该依靠其庞大的分支机构网络，从那些越来越多地将钱投入投资产品的人们那里获得更多的家庭储蓄，这加剧了该国银行存款增长缓慢的状况。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/rbi-says-banks-need-to-use-branches-to-draw-deposits-amid-crunch</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 05:55:03 GMT</pubDate>
